Revision history for App-YTDL


0.411   2020-08-16
        - Resolution 'manually': start the downloads only after the user has selected all formats.

0.410   2020-08-13
        - Use "Parallel::ForkManager" to enable the download of the additional information in parallel.
        - Update UI.

0.401   2020-07-22
        - Code refactoring.
        - New format for sticky and history files.
        - Bugfix in history sort.
        - Info output modification.

0.400   2020-07-21
        - Use 'youtube-dl' the fetch video info.
        - Bugfix: restore chosen file format after an error.
        - Bugfix in add_uploaders_to_history
        - Bugfix for the 'Search' entry in the list menu.

0.318   2020-03-31
        - Update option 'filename format info'.

0.317   2020-03-31
        - Update documentation.

0.316   2020-03-30
